## 9. Anti-Patterns (Banned)

| Anti-Pattern | Example | Why Banned |
|-------------|---------|------------|
| **New parallel store** | `lib/config-store.ts` instead of `ui/src/stores/config.ts` | Duplicates state logic, diverges from Control UI |
| **New parallel component** | `components/cockpit/ConfigForm.tsx` instead of consuming `ui/src/components/config-editor.tsx` | Duplicates form logic, misses upstream fixes |
| **Copy-paste fork** | Copying Control UI source into Cockpit repo | Loses upstream updates, creates maintenance burden |
| **Wrapper with logic** | Adding business logic in ThemeWrapper | Business logic belongs in Control UI, not rebrand layer |
| **Hardcoded colors** | Using hex/RGB instead of oklch custom properties | Breaks theme switching |

